| Trivia                  = * Following Knull's monologue at the start of the film, a newly-shot version of the post-credits scene from ''[[Spider-Man: No Way Home]]'' is shown. Aside from the allusion to Thanos and the events of ''[[Avengers: Infinity War]]'', all other references to Marvel Cinematic Universe characters and events are removed, including [[Peter Parker (Earth-199999)|Spider-Man]]. The scene also suggests that the reversal of [[Stephen Strange (Earth-199999)|Doctor Strange]]'s spell was not the reason for Eddie and Venom's return to [[Earth-688B|Earth-688]], retconning it to suggest instead that Knull was responsible.
* Some of the symbiotes in the third act resemble [[Phage]], [[Anti-Venom]], [[Lasher]] and [[Carnage (Symbiote) (Earth-1610)|Ultimate Carnage]] (and/or [[Rascal]]). According to the VX Team, they were dubbed Jim, Lasher, and Lava.<ref name="BourlandSymbiotes" /> Only the white symbiote was left without a name.
** Two symbiotes named Animal and Tendril fused creating a two headed symbiote. Their fusion could be a reference to [[Hybrid]].
